<h1>Creating Reusable Components</h1>

<p>The example below is taken from <a href="https://glamorous.rocks/examples/#button">Glamorous Community</a>. The highlighted lines show how variables can be used in the css.</p>

<MyButton OnClick="@onclick">Green Button</MyButton>
<MyButton OnClick="@onclick" Color="hotpink">Hotpink Button</MyButton>

